translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,38,"Twatite: “Tulukani mwalakwemo ŵanaose; naga chikanyyichilile chongoko chakuumila Kukwangu, basi ŵatakakuyeje chongoko Changucho ngaaja kuŵa niwoga soni ngaaja kuŵa ŵakudandaula.”"
  2,39,"“Nambo ŵandu ŵaakufuulu nikanila ma Ȃya Getu ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵa ku Moto, ŵanyao kwalakweko takaŵe ŵandamo.”"
  2,40,"E jenumanja ŵanache ŵa Israila! Kumbuchilani chindimba Changu chanampele, soni kwanisyani chilanga Changu None chingwanisye chilanga chenu, soni Jikape Une basi njogopani"
  2,41,"Soni ikulupililani yandulwisye (yayili m'Qur’an) yayikwitichisya yan'di nayo, ni nkaŵa ŵandanda kuikana; soni kasinsagulaga (ya duniya) ya ntengo wannono pa kusumanya ni ma Ȃya Gangu, soni Jikape Une basi njogopani"
  2,42,Soni nkawanganyaga yakuona ni yaunami ni kusisaga yakuona kutendaga jenumanja nchimanyililaga
  2,43,"Soni jimikani Swala mwakolosya nikutolaga Zaka, ni n’jinameje pamo ni akwinama"
  2,44,"Ana nkwachisya ŵandu ŵane yambone nikuliliŵalila mwachimisyene posepo jenumanja nkusomaga chitabu, ana ŵangali lunda"
  2,45,"Soni likamuchisyani pa kupilila ni pa (kuswali) Swala, soni chisimu jalakwejo jiŵele jausito ikaŵeje kwa ŵakulinandiya"
  2,46,"Aŵala ŵaakusimichisya kuti tachisimangana ni M’mbuje gwao (Allah), soni kuti ŵanganyao Kukwakwe chachiujila"
  2,47,"E jenumanja ŵanache ŵa Israila! Kumbuchilani chindimba Changu chanampele, soni nanchimbichisye kupunda iwumbe yosope (ya ndaŵi jenu)"
  2,48,"Ni lijogopani Lisiku lyangakomboleka mundu kunkamuchisya mundu jwine chilichose, soni ngasikukundidwa kutyochela kwa jwalakwejo kuchondelela, atamuno chaliwombolela chakuuma kukwakwe ngasichipocheledwa, soni ŵanganyao ngasaŵa ŵakulupusyidwa"